Class MyDLL<E>

java.lang.Object
implementations.MyDLL<E>
Type Parameters:
E - the type of elements stored in the list
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, ArrayListADT<E>
public class MyDLL<E> extends Object implements ArrayListADT<E>
MyDLL is an implementation of the ArrayListADT interface using a doubly linked list. It supports efficient insertions and deletions from both ends and provides indexed access to elements.
